nodes.first_para: Stores HTTP headers for each node.

nodes.title: NODE_TECHNOLOGIES
nodes.first_para: Stores detected technologies for each node.

nodes.title: NODE_VULNERABILITIES
nodes.first_para: Stores potential vulnerabilities for each node.

nodes.title: NODE_RELATIONSHIPS
nodes.first_para: Stores relationships between nodes for graph visualization.
